818
00:34:09,591 --> 00:34:13,122
Nothing travels faster
than Smallville gossip.

819
00:34:13,127 --> 00:34:15,491
Honey, I'm here if you
want to talk about it.

820
00:34:15,496 --> 00:34:17,196
I'm fine.

821
00:34:18,418 --> 00:34:20,219
