No.

942
00:39:57,625 --> 00:39:59,075
But I've gotta try.

943
00:39:59,080 --> 00:40:00,790
All right, I gotta run.

944
00:40:00,795 --> 00:40:03,034
- See you later, Coach.
- [CHUCKLES]

